subject: Little League World Series
lead_paragraph: Jack Quinn’s two-run double broke a 1-1 tie in the bottom of the fifth as the team from Fairfield, Conn., defeated Auburn, Wash., 3-1, in the first game of the Little League World Series in South Williamsport, Pa.
